Use Case UC1: Event Search

Scope: Join the event

Primary Actor: User

Preconditions: User is identified by name, surname, age and sex

Main Success Scenario:
-User selects, between free advertisement, the one which he's interested in;
-User obtains booking confirmation.

Main Unsuccess Scenario:
-User isn't interested in any event;
-User can't find any event;
-User can't join contemporary events.



